title: BRIEF-Prodware H1 EBITDA rises to 18.3 mln euros
text:
BRIEF-Prodware H1 EBITDA rises to 18.3 mln euros 
Oct 14 Prodware SA : 
* H1 net income group share 6.0 million euros ($6.9 million) versus 4.3 million euros year ago 
* H1 EBITDA of 18.3 million euros versus 17.2 million euros a year ago Source text: bit.ly/1Ow9E8G Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8745 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
